channel.title: Empty Feeling
channel.description:
as some of you may know, i am home schooled. because i am home schooled, i am home almost all day and it gets quite boring. it kind of gives me an empty feeling. like today, when my siblings were going to school, i felt empty. like a weird feeling. i really miss my old school. i hate getting home schooled because im at home so much and i dont get to see my friends. im like dying here. it sucks so bad. my parents seem to be the only ones that think home schooling is a good idea, and i have talked to many adults and friends. Im missing out on the social aspect of high schoool and it blows. and i have to deal with this till june. i have no idea how this is gonna work.
has anyone else gotten any empy feeling. where you feel like your missing something and it just doesnt feel right.
